.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48fce35d2b8c1ac9a34b83140b1a537d3a5810f","tid":2252321,"uid":123296,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:52:33.000Z","msg":"本地遊 本身都on9<br />\n我自己唔識去?又唔係語言不通<br />\n本地食野團就仲on9<br />\n除口罩食野，一個中招大家一齊中"},{"pid":"920af360b440740af6655658a428eb4bf440c43d","tid":2252321,"uid":81150,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:53:12.000Z","msg":"我拎去叫雞好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe893a3195f36adce9f9a04a610f65b0bb8c5eb","tid":2252321,"uid":98313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:55:05.000Z","msg":"離地到"},{"pid":"cb606e3d5b8f9795cf81613293b7e6a2e5fde512","tid":2252321,"uid":353256,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:55:56.000Z","msg":"去路德圍食個豆腐花3蚊，兩條友叫去隔離叫個腸粉頂多20蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639570346db39e1e197e174c9f86865e8ae97814","tid":2252321,"uid":113181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:03:06.000Z","msg":"直接外賣送黎我屋企咪煩啦"},{"pid":"479d8e91af5f47a87547bd2252a48b78b0d40efe","tid":2252321,"uid":51200,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b48fce35d2b8c1ac9a34b83140b1a537d3a5810f","tid":2252321,"uid":123296,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:52:33.000Z","msg":"本地遊 本身都on9<br />\n我自己唔識去?又唔係語言不通<br />\n本地食野團就仲on9<br />\n除口罩食野，一個中招大家一齊中"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:06:32.000Z","msg":"唔係既，之前有啲本地深度遊<br />\n講香港歷史/二次世界大戰史，有個導遊一路講解一路帶你去行啲遺跡，<br />\n其實幾抵比<br />\n<br />\n之後又參加過劏房團，d導遊真係好好，講得好詳細<br />\n之後順手去深水埗講吓歷史<br />\n同埋以前唐樓的風格<br />\n真係好正<br />\n<br />\n不過旅發局呢啲美食團一聽就知戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7a38a5da4b2c2a1e6efdb